                 No. "Quickly"  
                 is the adverb  

15:41.675 --> 15:43.341
           modifying            
           the verb "to learn". 

15:43.343 --> 15:45.243
             "I learn quickly." 
             Begin again.       

15:45.245 --> 15:47.578
Uh, all my teachers             
say that                        

15:47.580 --> 15:49.280
I'm bright                      
and a good worker.              

15:49.282 --> 15:51.716
You won't regret                
for a moment hiring me.         

15:51.718 --> 15:53.351
                  Excellent.    

15:53.353 --> 15:54.719
                 Much better.   

15:54.721 --> 15:56.054
                   A local?     

15:56.056 --> 15:59.123
Uh, no, we summer here.         

15:59.125 --> 16:00.725
