       -[Lenore scoffs]         
        -But go ahead,          

20:26.392 --> 20:27.592
            cut somebody else's.

20:27.594 --> 20:30.428
       -[Lenore] Marty.         
            -Right?             

20:30.430 --> 20:31.963
                Hello?          

20:33.499 --> 20:35.333
                 Okay.          

