<i>But this time I went prepared.</i>  

28:01.380 --> 28:03.080
                         Robert.

28:03.082 --> 28:04.815
I'm sorry                       
I'm late, Dr. Kahn.             

28:04.817 --> 28:09.053
There was a slight technical    
malfunction with my alarm.      

28:09.055 --> 28:11.088
Uh, I know                      
that's not an excuse--          

28:11.090 --> 28:12.990
                 Not a good one.

28:12.992 --> 28:15.125
But I'm willing                 
to make it up to you            

28:15.127 --> 28:16.727
and I promise                   
it won't happen again.          

28:16.729 --> 28:19.029
            Well, it's too late.
            The job is mine.    

28:19.031 --> 28:21.298
      I did not say that.       

28:22.234 --> 28:24.968
                 You can't      
                 let him do it. 

28:24.970 --> 28:27.104
               It's my job, Doc.

28:27.106 --> 28:28.972
               I mean,          
               look at this kid.

28:30.009 --> 28:31.875
I-I'll fix it.                  
On my dime.                     

28:31.877 --> 28:34.278
I-I'll do better.               
I promise.                      

28:34.280 --> 28:36.780
  Oh, listen to him beg, Doc.   

28:37.483 --> 28:39.783
  What I'm hearing is someone   

28:39.785 --> 28:42.319
        who is willing          
    to take responsibility.     

28:42.321 --> 28:44.254
      Your lack of which        
         is why I had           

28:44.256 --> 28:47.825
 to hire your replacement here  
      in the first place.       

28:47.827 --> 28:50.360
                 At least I know
                 what I'm doing.

28:50.362 --> 28:52.463
      Good day, William.        

28:56.869 --> 28:59.803
          This is your          
          second chance, Robert.

29:03.175 --> 29:07.845
        Unlike baseball batters,
        you do not get a third. 

29:11.016 --> 29:12.850
             [¶¶]               

29:16.255 --> 29:18.222
           [Robert]             
<i>That afternoon I cut the grass</i>  

29:18.224 --> 29:20.791
         <i> like it was</i>           
<i>every thin person I'd ever met.</i> 

29:29.869 --> 29:31.502
       [Bobby grunting]         

