to continue--                   

30:05.104 --> 30:07.938
strictly on                     
a trial basis, of course--      

30:07.940 --> 30:10.841
but I can only pay you          
one dollar per hour.            

30:15.581 --> 30:18.849
I think that's                  
very reasonable, don't you?     

30:20.052 --> 30:22.286
                   [sighs]      
                   Yes, sir.    

30:23.923 --> 30:25.222
Tomorrow morning.               

30:25.224 --> 30:27.291
 9:00 a.m.                      

30:27.293 --> 30:29.059
  Sharp.                        

30:34.333 --> 30:36.967
             [¶¶]               

30:39.505 --> 30:41.371
           [Robert]             
   <i> By the end of the week,</i>     

30:41.373 --> 30:44.274
     <i> Dr. Kahn had rehired</i>      
       <i> some extra help.</i>        

30:44.276 --> 30:46.877
        <i> I didn't know</i>          
 <i> if it was some sort of test,</i>  

30:46.879 --> 30:49.146
        <i> but this time</i>          
      <i> I didn't feel like</i>       

30:49.148 --> 30:51.315
<i>running away from a challenge.</i>  

31:00.259 --> 31:02.593
          <i> This time</i>            
  <i> I had something to prove.</i>    

31:25.551 --> 31:27.918
          Looks like            
  you're still doing my job.    

31:27.920 --> 31:29.553
          [chuckles]            

31:39.131 --> 31:41.064
      And I want it back.       

31:47.339 --> 31:50.374
         [laughs]               

31:50.376 --> 31:52.142
          I got you.            

31:53.345 --> 31:57.648
           The waste            
     goes in the compost.       

32:00.185 --> 32:02.419
      See ya.                   

32:02.421 --> 32:06.089
  [screen door opens, closes]   

32:27.713 --> 32:29.479
           [groans]             

32:31.216 --> 32:33.050
          [Dr. Kahn]            
      You're still here?        

32:34.153 --> 32:35.552
     Uh...                      

32:37.323 --> 32:39.323
Just finishing up.              

32:39.325 --> 32:41.558
Uh, what would you              
like me to do next?             

32:42.461 --> 32:43.994
            Sweep the porch,    

32:43.996 --> 32:46.330
            wash the trash cans,
            clean the gutters.  

32:46.332 --> 32:47.998
           Look around you.     

32:48.000 --> 32:50.067
           A man who's worth    
           what he's paid       

32:50.069 --> 32:51.969
           uses some initiative.

32:51.971 --> 32:53.670
     Yes, sir.                  

32:56.141 --> 32:58.642
             [¶¶]               

33:21.233 --> 33:22.666
             Hey!               

33:22.668 --> 33:24.234
   Hey, what are you doing?!    
         I'm up here!           

33:24.236 --> 33:26.003
        [men laughing]          

33:26.005 --> 33:27.204
          Come on...            

33:27.206 --> 33:29.039
                   Bye-bye...   

33:42.321 --> 33:44.621
          [grunting]            

34:04.043 --> 34:06.410
              What are you doing
              in here?          

34:06.412 --> 34:08.545
   I, uh...                     

