Uh, the ladder fell out.        

34:15.187 --> 34:16.686
I was stuck on the roof         
and I couldn't get down.        

34:16.688 --> 34:19.255
            Ladders don't fall  
            of their own accord.

34:19.257 --> 34:21.291
        What have you got there?

34:22.628 --> 34:26.096
   Uh, I cleaned out            
   the gutters and I...         

34:26.098 --> 34:28.799
I didn't want to drop 'em       
on your flowers.                

34:31.235 --> 34:34.571
                Well, you're    
                definitely slow,

34:34.572 --> 34:37.239
                but you are     
                conscientious   

34:37.242 --> 34:40.543
           and that is something
