           So that means        
           at the end of Monday 

35:21.787 --> 35:23.687
                you owed me     
                three dollars.  

35:23.689 --> 35:26.590
              Tuesday, according
              to our agreement, 

35:26.592 --> 35:28.225
            you did not get paid

35:28.227 --> 35:30.760
         because you had        
         to re-do Monday's work.

35:30.762 --> 35:33.597
   [Robert] <i> I'm pretty sure</i>     
    <i> that some minimum wage</i>     

35:33.599 --> 35:36.600
