     -Can I put him back?       

40:22.954 --> 40:25.622
No. That's not                  
how it works, Mom.              

40:28.827 --> 40:31.528
     You sure everything's      
        okay with you?          

40:31.530 --> 40:33.196
Yeah, I'm sure.                 

40:33.198 --> 40:35.598
         You'd tell me          
  if it wasn't, wouldn't you?   

40:39.704 --> 40:41.604
            What about Dad?     

40:41.606 --> 40:43.173
         Who?                   

40:44.209 --> 40:45.608
       I'm kidding.             

40:45.610 --> 40:47.143
   He's staying in the city.    

40:47.145 --> 40:49.946
            He has              
    a big project at work.      

40:49.948 --> 40:52.649
         Apparently...          

40:52.651 --> 40:54.083
     What about you, Mom?       

40:54.085 --> 40:56.085
         Are you sure           
  everything's okay with you?   

41:00.459 --> 41:03.159
         You'd tell me          
  if it wasn't, wouldn't you?   

41:08.967 --> 41:13.069
             [¶¶]               

41:17.242 --> 41:22.045
       [Lenore speaking         
     indistinctly within]       

41:25.484 --> 41:27.717
[Lenore] Well then, I don't have
    anything else to say...     

41:27.719 --> 41:29.486
      [phone slams down]        

41:43.001 --> 41:45.702
           [sobbing]            

41:57.816 --> 42:00.149
      [people chattering]       

