42:51.903 --> 42:54.203
What do you want me to say?     

42:55.206 --> 42:57.941
                 That it's gonna
                 to be okay.    

42:57.943 --> 42:59.943
It's gonna to be okay.          

42:59.945 --> 43:01.277
                 Now, why don't 
                 I believe you? 

43:01.279 --> 43:02.712
  [chuckles]                    

43:05.951 --> 43:07.951
              Do you think Dad's
              having an affair? 

43:07.953 --> 43:09.586
  Don't say that.               

43:09.588 --> 43:11.955
It's possible.                  

43:11.957 --> 43:13.723
                Where do you get
                this stuff, huh?

43:13.725 --> 43:16.092
       Mark Taylor's dad started
       getting "busy" at work   

43:16.094 --> 43:18.027
              and it turned out 
              he was, you know, 

43:18.029 --> 43:19.829
              getting "busy"    
              with a secretary. 

43:19.831 --> 43:23.032
  [men in distance] Come on!    
  Come on! Come on! Come on!    

43:23.034 --> 43:24.067
Dad's not like that.            

43:24.069 --> 43:25.802
            Well, something's up

43:25.804 --> 43:27.704
         or else Mom wouldn't   
         have left for the city.

43:27.706 --> 43:28.738
   Really?                      

43:28.740 --> 43:30.740
            Wait, for how long? 

43:30.742 --> 43:32.609
 Monday.                        

43:34.879 --> 43:36.980
Do you have                     
any plans tonight?              

43:36.982 --> 43:38.348
               Some TV, I guess.

43:38.350 --> 43:40.850
         Probably               
         just sacking out early.

43:40.852 --> 43:42.318
  Why?                          

43:42.320 --> 43:44.053
           Listen, if Mom calls 
           and I'm not back yet,

43:44.055 --> 43:45.622
             just tell her      
             I'm asleep, okay?  

43:46.224 --> 43:47.390
               We're here again?

43:47.392 --> 43:49.092
You did it before.              

